## Objective
Enhance the shared types to accommodate the deeply parsed data so the frontend can define its consumption flow.

## Requirements
- Update `types.ts` in the `shared` module.
- Update the `Project` interface to include fields from `project.config.yml` (e.g., stack, guardians).
- Flesh out `Sprint` and `Task` parsing types based on the payloads that `S02-T3-ApiEndpoints` will expose.
- Export these definitions clearly for frontend consumption.
